OL,3,CBurnham and Streeting hit back at Tony
OL,4,CBlair's criticism of Labour
OL,6,FLabour leadership hopefuls Wes
OL,7,FStreeting and Andy Burnham have both
OL,8,Fhit back at former Prime Minister Tony
OL,9,FBlair, after he criticised the
OL,10,Fgovernment in a 5,700-word essay.
OL,12,FBlair, the only Labour leader to have
OL,13,Fwon three general elections, wrote
OL,14,Fthat the party needs a "fundamental
OL,15,Freset" and is "playing with the future
OL,16,Fof the country" in the piece,
OL,17,Fpublished via the Tony Blair Institute
OL,18,Ffor Global Change on Wednesday.
OL,26,@vD@XOUwD@FO]
