OL,3,CBurnham and Streeting hit back at Tony
OL,4,CBlair's criticism of Labour
OL,6,FHe warned the party against forcing
OL,7,Fout Prime Minister Keir Starmer, and
OL,8,Fsaid the government had held back
OL,9,Fbusiness and growth since it won the
OL,10,Felection in 2024.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FBurnham, who is currently campaigning
OL,18,Fahead of the Makerfield by-election on
OL,19,FJune 18, said Blair had misunderstood
OL,20,Fthe economic causes of populism in his
OL,21,Fessay.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
