OL,3,CBurnham and Streeting hit back at Tony
OL,4,CBlair's criticism of Labour
OL,6,F"He doesn't mention inequality once,"
OL,7,Fthe Greater Manchester Mayor told The
OL,8,FObserver in response.
OL,10,F"If you don't get how that's driving
OL,11,Fpolitics now, if you are not rooting
OL,12,Fyour analysis in the fact that people
OL,13,Fare unable to live and that things
OL,14,Fthat were taken for granted are no
OL,15,Flonger affordable, then you are not
OL,16,Funderstanding what's going on."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
