OL,3,CBurnham and Streeting hit back at Tony
OL,4,CBlair's criticism of Labour
OL,6,FBurnham went on to argue that voters
OL,7,Fhad turned to the ends of the
OL,8,Fpolitical spectrum - supporting either
OL,9,FNigel Farage's Reform UK or Zack
OL,10,FPolanski's Green Party - because the
OL,11,Fcentre had let them down.
OL,13,F"People don't think the centre has
OL,14,Fdelivered for them in terms of their
OL,15,Flives, therefore they've gone further
OL,16,Fto the extremes," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
