OL,3,CBurnham and Streeting hit back at Tony
OL,4,CBlair's criticism of Labour
OL,6,FBurnham is expected to launch a Labour
OL,7,Fleadership bid if he successfully
OL,8,Fbecomes the next Makerfield MP, and
OL,9,Fcould find himself facing off against
OL,10,FStreeting, who confirmed he would
OL,11,Fstand in any race to become prime
OL,12,Fminister.
OL,14,FStreeting also issued a response to
OL,15,FBlair on Wednesday, telling the former
OL,16,FPM that the answer to global
OL,17,Fdisruption "cannot be longing for the
OL,18,FBritain of the 1970s, nor even the
OL,19,FBritain of the 1990s".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
