CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779981070
OL,3,CBurnham and Streeting hit back at Tony
OL,4,CBlair's criticism of Labour
OL,6,FIn an opinion piece for The Guardian,
OL,7,FStreeting described inequality as the
OL,8,F"defining issue of our age" and said
OL,9,FBlair's essay had treated it as a
OL,10,F"peripheral rather than fundamental"
OL,11,Ftopic.
OL,13,F"When people believe the rules no
OL,14,Flonger reward effort fairly,
OL,15,Fresentment grows. And resentment never
OL,16,Fremains politically homeless for
OL,17,Flong," the former health secretary
OL,18,Fwrote.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
