PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779981070
OL,3,CBurnham and Streeting hit back at Tony
OL,4,CBlair's criticism of Labour
OL,6,FStreeting went on to say that Britain
OL,7,Fmust "stand firmly with democratic
OL,8,Fallies who share our values", but
OL,9,Fdenied the nation should be
OL,10,Fsubservient to the US, stating that
OL,11,Fits long-term future "lies in Europe".
OL,13,FBlair had written in his essay that
OL,14,Fthe government should not have stopped
OL,15,Fthe US from using its RAF bases during
OL,16,Fits attacks on Iran, and he cautioned
OL,17,Fagainst a push to rejoin the European
OL,18,FUnion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
