PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779981070
OL,3,CBurnham and Streeting hit back at Tony
OL,4,CBlair's criticism of Labour
OL,6,F"When US presidents flirt with
OL,7,Fauthoritarian leaders, undermine
OL,8,Finternational law or pursue reckless
OL,9,Fmilitary adventurism, Britain must
OL,10,Fhave the confidence to act
OL,11,Findependently," Streeting said.
OL,13,F"We learned at terrible cost in Iraq
OL,14,Fwhat happens when loyalty replaces
OL,15,Fjudgment."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
