OL,3,CBurnham and Streeting hit back at Tony
OL,4,CBlair's criticism of Labour
OL,6,FThe Workers Rights Bill, an
OL,7,F"acceleration of net-zero", and
OL,8,Fphasing out of British oil and gas
OL,9,Falso came under particular fire from
OL,10,Fthe former prime minister.
